Definition: a rigorously controlled test of a new drug or a new invasive medical device on human subjects
Example: in the United States it is conducted under the direction of the FDA before being made available for general clinical use
Synonyms: clinical_test, test, a, rigorously, controlled, of, new, drug, or, invasive, medical, device, on, human, subjects, in, the, United, States, it, is, conducted, under, direction, FDA, before, being, made, available, for, general, clinical, use
Category: noun.act
